metadata.title: AirPods 2 Case - Techcircle Colorful Premium PU Leather Portable Protective Cover Case with Metal Keychain for AirPods 2nd Generation & 1st Generation Charging Case, Couple Owl
features: 【AIRPODS PROTECTIVE CASE】: This portable protective cover is designed for Airpods charging case. Ideal gift for women and girls.
【PREMIUM MATERIAL】: Made of premium PU leather, interior with soft non-scratch microfiber, protect your AirPods and charging case from dirt and impacts.
【PORTABLE KEYCHAIN】: Keychain easily attaches to your bag, backpack or purse, enables you to have your AirPods handy at all times, without fear of setting them down and losing them.
【PERFECT FIT】: Precise cutout on the bottom for easy access to the charging port, without removing the leather case.
【MAGNETIC CLOSURE】: Convenient and magnetic buckle for easy in opening and closing.
